      <scopecontent id="aspace_1331732cf882fc079bafc20ddbe364d3">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of correspondence from World War II servicemen from Silliman College (Yale) to the master of the college, F. S. C. Northrop, and his wife. Also included are an address book and miscellaneous printed materials documenting wartime activities of Yale servicemen.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
